GLOBAL_LATENCY_DESCRIPTION: change GLOBAL_LATENCY to your lowest usual ping
UNSPOOF_CABLE_STEP_DESCRIPTION_2: this can be toggled on and off by typing cablesteptoggle in chat
SLOW_GRIM_DESCRIPTION: Slows GrimStrike if used after another GrimStrike, can be used to stop accidental second hit cancels. Toggle with slowgrim1 command.
SLOW_GRIM_AMOUNT_DESCRIPTION: How many seconds to slow GrimStrike by if SLOW_GRIM is enabled. This scales with ASPD.
CABLE_FIX_DESCRIPTION: Some bosses appear to not function correctly with cable position emulation. This turns the feature off.
RECALL_GRIM_DESCRIPTION: Auto grim once after recall scythe.
NO_RECALL_GRIM_IN_REAPING_DESCRIPTION: If recall grim is enabled and this option is enabled, it won't activate in shadow reaping.
GRIM_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for grimstrike, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax.
GRIM_DELAY_DESCRIPTION: Delay for how long in milliseconds before RECALL_GRIM macro goes off.
TRUE_GRIM_DELAY_DESCRIPTION: Turn this option on if grim macro skips recall scythe even with GRIM_DELAY increased.
REAPING_X_DESCRIPTION: Auto use X_KEY when Shadow Reaping is used. X_KEY must be set. This macro does not work without ROBOTJS.
X_KEY_DESCRIPTION: X Key. Find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
Y_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Y Key (keep the same as X_KEY if you don't want a second skill to activate). Find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
Z_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Z Key (keep the same as X_KEY if you don't want a second skill to activate). Find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax
GRIM_HARVEST_DESCRIPTION: Auto grim strike into dark harvest.
HARVEST_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for Dark Harvest, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax.
SUNDER_RECALL_DESCRIPTION: Auto sunder strike into recall scythe.
RECALL_KEY_DESCRIPTION: Key for recall scythe, find keyboard syntax list here http://robotjs.io/docs/syntax.
